# ✨ Figma + Supabase Client Insights App

This is a prototype of a lightweight client insights dashboard built using [Figma Make](https://www.figma.com/) and connected to [Supabase](https://supabase.com/) as the backend database.

## 🛠️ Tools Used
- **Figma Make**: For frontend UI/UX design and prototyping
- **Supabase**: Open-source backend as a service (BaaS) to store and retrieve structured data

## 📊 Features
- Browse client profiles and AI-generated insights
- Dynamic updates via Supabase tables
- Clean, minimal design with a focus on readability

